Hi Long
June 8

HNG DN ADD TOKEN VO PANEL GET LINK GOOGL DRIVE.
Cho mi ngi,
Nh ln trc ni, bn mnh khng th account cho cc bn nn phng n cui l mi ngi t in account vo cho hp l vi lng request ca website. 1 account trung bnh s c 500 lt request / 24h.
Trong panel s c thng k lt request t account v tool s cn bng lt get cho mi account, lc no cng ly account c lt get thp nht get link cho n 500 lt th dng li. Bn cng c ...th xa account v c th dng account Gsuite hoc account thng. Account Gsuite th get c ipbits=0 (play all IP) account thng th ipbits=128 (play only ipv4)
Sau y l hng dn cch ly token trong panel:
1. Ti extensions cookies.txt cho chrome ti y: https://goo.gl/ywZbw9 v cho n chy ch n danh.
2. M tab n danh v truy cp vo https://goo.gl/jgXINh sau login ti khon google m mun ly token. Login xong n s chuyn n trang c thng bo "One moment please...", khng cn quan tm n n, bn click vo biu tng ca extensions ci bc 1. Ch phn "oauth_code", bn copy value tng ng ny. (xem hnh 1)
3. Copy value xong bn vo: https://videoapi.io/panel/tools/get_token_google_drive
( trang ny c phn bn nhp token name, oauth code get token v phn qun l token add vo.)
Add vo th phn token name bn tn gi nh cho token, khuyn khch tn mail lun cho d nh. Phn oauth code th bn paste vo ci value va copy 2 sau nhn GET. (xem hnh 2).
Nu get thnh cng th n bo thnh cng v thng tin ca token mi add c, nu khng th s bo li.
Mi ngi test th c g comment bo mnh nh.
